author: andreas
msg: Copy RCML files and backup files when copying a node to a different area. This should fix bug 42317.

author: bnicholes
msg: re-introduce ap_satisfies API back into core and modify how the access_checker, check_user_id and auth_checker hooks are called so that they respect the precedence that is set through the satisfy ALL/ANY directive. This also restores the directives order, allow, deny, satisfyas supported directives rather than being deprecated.  These directives still remain in mod_access_compat however.
